<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>There is a lot of including in zend framework. To speedup the framework you should use the line:</p>

<p>class_exists(%classname%, false) || include %file%</p>

<p>is faster than include_once after the first time you try to include_once a file</p>

<p>same for require_once of course</p>

    </div>
